assessments.description:
Three minute video presentation on a recent performance experience. Include:
i) personal introduction (20 seconds);
ii) explanation of the recent experience, including why you have chosen it (40 seconds); 
iii) reflection on the experience and what you have learned from this experience and others about yourself (1 minute) and;
iv) how you might further optimise your own personal practice.. 1000 words (equivalent)
